properties.comment: Model parameter definition ========================== Model : Pump Type : Example Parameters ---------- PressureSamples [Pa] Array of operation points for the pump FlowRateSamples [m^3/s] Array of corresponding flow rate to the given pressure samples ElectricalPower [W] Electrical power of the pump if running Material [-] Structural material EfficiencySamples [-] Pump efficiency samples MassMotor [kg] Structural mass MassFluid [kg] Fluid mass HasMotorCooling [-] Indication whether the motor is cooled IsSubmerged [-] Indication whether the pump is submerged or not DiameterPump [m] Pump diameter LengthPump [m] Pump length DiameterMotor [m] Motor diameter LengthMotor [m] Motor length MaxTemperatureDifference [K] Maximum temperature diff twds. amb. NominalRotSpeed [rpm] Nominal rotational speed NumberImpellerEyes [-] Number of impeller eyes NumberStages [-] Number of pump stages Nominal Flow Rate [m3/s] Structural mas NominalPressure [Pa] Nominal pressure
